SUMMARY:Start Managing Your Business Finances
DESCRIPTION:Hosted by Partner Community Capital\, Part One of the Small Business & Entrepreneur’s Financial Success Series covers basic business finances. \nJoin us in this virtual workshop to learn about the basics of business finance\, including essential accounting concepts\, the chart of accounts\, and a comparison of the pros and cons of popular software options. \nThis workshop is designed for start-ups\, new business owners\, and anyone who wants to take control of their business finances. The workshop will provide a solid overview of business finances. Sound financial practices are key to getting your business ready for funding.
URL:https://wvbusinesslink.com/event/start-managing-your-business-finances/
CATEGORIES:Business Training,entrepreneur education,Finance
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://wvbusinesslink.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/Header-image-2026-Virtual-Workshop-1.png
ORGANIZER;CN="Partner Community Capital":MAILTO:largento@partnercapital.org
END:VEVENT
